div(class="bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] p-4 rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] my-8")
  h3(class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[var(--text-primary)]") Редактор схемы помещения

  div(class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6")

    div(class="lg:w-1/2")
      canvas(
        id="room-canvas",
        width="500",
        height="400",
        class="w-full border border-[var(--border)] rounded-lg bg-[var(--bg-primary)] touch-none",
        style="touch-action: none;"
      )
      div(class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-between items-center mt-4")
        p(class="text-xs text-[var(--text-secondary)]") * Кликните на холсте, чтобы добавить точки. Замкните контур двойным кликом.
        div(class="flex gap-2")
          button(
            type="button",
            id="clear-btn",
            class="px-3 py-1 bg-red-500 text-white rounded text-sm hover:opacity-90 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-700"
          ) Очистить
          button(
            type="button",
            id="undo-btn",
            class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-600 text-white rounded text-sm hover:opacity-90 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-500"
          ) Отменить

      div(id="room-stats", class="mt-4 p-3 bg-[var(--bg-primary)] rounded-lg border border-[var(--border)]")
        p(class="font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)]") Статистика:
        div(id="stats-text", class="text-sm text-[var(--text-secondary)] space-y-1")
          span Пока не заданы точки

    div(class="lg:w-1/2")
      div(class="overflow-x-auto")
        table(class="w-full text-sm border-collapse")
          thead
            tr(class="border-b border-[var(--border)]")
              th(class="text-left py-2 text-[var(--text-primary)]") Стена
              th(class="text-left py-2 text-[var(--text-primary)]") Длина (м)
              th(class="text-left py-2 text-[var(--text-primary)]") Тип работы
          tbody(id="walls-table")
            tr
              td(colspan="3", class="text-center text-[var(--text-secondary)] py-4") Нарисуйте помещение, чтобы увидеть стены

      button(
        type="button",
        id="save-btn",
        class="mt-6 w-full bg-[var(--accent)] text-[var(--bg-primary)] py-2 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[var(--accent)] focus:ring-offset-2"
      ) Сохранить схему для сметы

script(src="/js/room-editor.js")